Advanced Composite Technology and Maestro Suspension-a match made in heaven when it comes to XC performance. Engineers started with a composite main triangle; which includes the all-new OverDrive 2 headtube; MegaDrive downtube and PowerCore bottom bracket and mated it to a stiff; lightweight and incredibly durable aluminum rear triangle. The result is a high-performance XC bike that’s up to the task of riding and racing week in and week out.RELATED MODELS;
